 Create maven web project
 Add Tomcat
 	right click on project-> build path-> add library-> server library-> tomcat
 Download database jar file
 edit pom.xml--> add hibernate-core and database jar file as depencies
 edit hibernate.cfg.xml file -> add database path
 create a package in src
 	create a class with annotations
 	create a service class to add bean in database
 create jsp pages in src -> web folder
 	
 
 	